      <h2 class="about-bio-text-header">Hello there! I’m Emily and I have PCOS too.</h2>
      <p class="about-bio-text">I’m a registered dietitian and wellness coach too. I help people with PCOS find ways to lose weight, while improving their hormone balance, gut health, and inflammation through:</p>
      <ul class="about-ulist">
        <li>1) NO scales.</li>
        <li>2) NO diets.</li>
        <li>3) NO judgment.</li>
        <li>4) Just small nutrition and lifestyle modifications + mindset work to build healthy habits that easily fit into YOUR lifestyle… and STICK!</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="about-bio-text">For almost a decade, I have been empowering people with PCOS to find solutions to help them take control of their health. Many of them had the same story as me…</p>
